data.description: A Must See Cul-de-sac Easton Model Custom 2 Story Home With Rare Double Sliding Door Walk-Out Basement, Backs To Beautiful Golf Course Views And Amazing View Of The Pond. Large Windows With Abundance Of Natural Light, Vaulted Living Room, A Dining Room, Large Family Room, Kitchen with Eating Area, Pantry And Wood Sliding Door To Deck, Dramatic 2 Story Foyer With An Impressive Staircase. Upstairs Has A Wonderful Master Bedroom With Attached Full Bathroom that Has Shower, Bath Tub And Double Sink, 3 Other Good Sized Bedrooms Along With One Full Bathroom. Partial Finished Walkout Basement With Toilet Room And Sliding Doors To Patio, Fenced Yard, 2 Car Garage That Has Extra Space For Storage. Close To Route 58, 72, I-90 And Wood Filed Mall. Newer Paint.
